-- McGeorge to Step Down as Matalan Chief Executive Officer, Independent Says
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2010-09-30T01:45:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/mcgeorge-to-step-down-as-matalan-chief-executive-officer-independent-says.html
Matalan Ltd.  Chief Executive
Officer  Alistair McGeorge  is to step down and will begin
relinquishing his responsibilities as CEO from the end of next
month, the Independent reported, without attribution.  The company hopes to have hired a replacement by about
January, the newspaper said. Matalan declined to comment, the
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Ben Martin  in London at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Livesey at 
 blivesey@bloomberg.net . 